<p>Also in the commercial was Panera Bread's chief food innovation officer, Chef Claes Petersson, who admitted he was 'obsessed with the flavor combination.'</p>

<p>'It's an insanely craveable and irresistible creation that our customers nationwide are sure to love,' the Swedish foodie gushed.</p>

<p>Expect more menu mash-ups and combinations in the future as Panera has reportedly 'pledged to make 50% of its menu vegan or vegetarian over the next several years.'</p>

